Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.64,1:06:26.88,Default,>> Yeah, so the question\Nis: If I did have a way
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.88,1:06:28.35,Default,to set elasticity in my app,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.60,1:06:31.65,Default,should I definitely not\Nset them in my settings?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.78,1:06:33.58,Default,I would say not necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.65,1:06:35.86,Default,Like, for example,\Nyou might want to --
